Privacy Policy for Cocktails Guru
Introduction
1. Data We Collect
We collect the following types of information:
User ID
Name
Profile picture
2. How We Use Your Data
Your data is used to:
Facilitate account creation and logon process.
Enable you to participate in the interactive features of our app such as liking, commenting, and rating cocktails.
3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to maintain and provide the Cocktails Guru services.
4. Data Retention We will only retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes we collected it for.
5. Your Rights
You have the right to request access, correction, deletion, or transfer of your personal data. Please use the following link for data deletion requests:
https://forms.gle/hCVHhg9Tu7AFBbTU6
6. Contact Us
For any questions or concerns regarding your privacy, please contact us at customerservice@heryson.com.